  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to assess the maximum tolerated dose, safety and
      pharmacokinetics of an investigational drug, intravenous (IV) citrulline, in subjects in
      steady-state sickle cell disease.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
